name: Softing Data File
summary: An SDFI file is an encrypted data file created by Softing Industrial dataFEED exporter. It contains a Siemens Totally Integrated Automation (TIA) project, exported from TIA for use with Softing applications. SDFI files can be imported into Softing Industrial products such as edgeConnectors, uaGates, or the dataFEED OPC Suite.
